<L>__{interior men's latrines same time day}
<A>__{an arm held out to either side, the small girl lowers herself into a pit into which men have defecated. she works her way slowly down, trying to find knee and toeholds on the foul walls, ignoring the flies invading her ears, her nostrils. reaching the surface of the muck she lets her feet submerge, then her ankles, her shins, her knees, before finally touching harder ground. as she struggles to slow her breathing, her racing heart, she hears a hallucinatory murmur }
